<p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 233); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">家风是文化传承的鲜明旗帜，是代代相传的精神滋养；家人是常伴我们岁岁年年的港湾，是我们心底最温暖的存在。在新学期即将到来之</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 233); text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">际，学班积极开展了<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“争做家中顶梁柱—我为家人做件事”</span></strong>主题活动，弘扬优良家风家训，发扬光大中华民族传统家庭美德，带动更多的同学重视家风家训，传承优良美德。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 233); text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEIZHPicqGZs6LL0QqEnwXYAv0wGaww8icoYv646rPTj0yDUV67icgouOb4yZj0LoDicZibYEp5mrhQshiaQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="291" height="188" style="width: 291px; height: 188px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 233); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(33, 33, 34); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“在本次活动中，我利用视频的方式记录了新年前后我在家里做的一些小事。例如每次饭后的洗碗收拾厨房、拖地、积极参与外婆为过年而准备的豆腐泡红薯片，还有年前大扫除。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 233); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(33, 33, 34); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这些不只是为活动而做，这是我每年在家时真实记录，尽管有些的事情并未来得及用手机记录。每每有来家里玩的亲戚看见就会夸我们懂事，知道主动帮忙做事，外婆就会很自豪的说，“对啊，只要这几个小的在家，这些事情都不需要她动手。”外婆自豪，我们也开心，我会一直保持下去，也会让自己从各方面做的更好！”</span></p><p><br/></p>